@node DARKH "Dark Heart of the Wood"

@{b}Dark Heart of the Wood@{ub}

Color   = Black/Green
Rarity  = DK(C3)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = BG
Artist  = Christopher Rush

Text(DK): You may sacrifice a forest to gain 3 life. Counts as both a
          black card and a green card.

Flavor Text: @{i}Even the Goblins shun this haunted place, where the
             tree limbs twist in agony and the ground seems to
             scuttle under your feet.@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_D.guide/DWOOD}

@endnode
